1. Imam gomilu starih *žica* u garaži. (I have a pile of old *wires* in the garage.)
2. Molim te da ne diraš *žice* dok ne isključim struju. (Please don't touch the *wires* until I turn off the power.)
3. *Žice* na ovom instrumentu su prekratke. (The *strings* on this instrument are too short.)
4. Električar je zamenio sve *žice* u kući. (The electrician replaced all the *wires* in the house.)
5. Zbog snega su se *žice* na banderi otkinule. (Due to the snow, the *wires* on the pole broke off.)
6. Svirač na ulici je skupljao novac u *žicama* svog instrumenta. (The street musician was collecting money in the *strings* of his instrument.)
7. *Žice* na mom biciklu su se istrošile. (The *brake cables* on my bike have worn out.)
8. Moramo da nabavimo još nekoliko *žica* da završimo ogradu. (We need to get a few more *fencing wires* to finish the fence.)
9. *Žice* na ovoj mašini su previše labave. (The *cords* on this machine are too loose.)
10. Pogledaj koliko ima *žica* na tom ogromnom mostu. (Look at how many *steel cables* there are on that huge bridge.)